<div class="panel" id="panel-sources">
<div class="card">
<h2>Source Library</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">These are reliable, well-established sources. Use the filters below to find sources relevant to your priority. Most sources are useful for more than one priority — look at the tags.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--muted);">You don't need to use all of these. For a strong paper, aim for <strong>4–6 sources</strong> that give you real evidence for your argument.</p>
</div>

```
