<div class="source-org">World Bank</div>
<div class="source-desc">Economic and social data for every country: GDP, GNI, poverty rates, education spending, healthcare spending, Gini coefficient (inequality measure). Particularly useful for the equality priority — you can compare how much countries invest in their people.</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="source-card" data-tags="general">
<div class="source-icon">😊</div>
<div>
<div class="source-tags">
<span class="source-tag general">General</span>
</div>
