<div class="source-desc">Rates 208 countries on political rights and civil liberties. Categories include electoral process, freedom of expression, rule of law, and personal autonomy. The 2026 report found global freedom declined for the 20th consecutive year. Useful for arguing why freedoms matter — or for showing how fragile they are.</div>
