<div class="source-desc">Uses 87 indicators of personal and economic freedom covering rule of law, security, movement, religion, expression, and economic freedom. Finds a strong link between freedom, income, and well-being. Top 10 includes Switzerland, Denmark, New Zealand, Ireland, and Finland.</div>
